cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

The paper deals with reinforcement learning algorithms and generative models in visual environments. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves simulated robotics applications, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics) and uses neural networks, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
